A Gatundu doctor has been charged with rape.Dr Lawrence Wachira is accused of raping his patient Carol Makari at his Rapha Medical Clinic in Kiamwangi on July 17 last year.He appeared before Gatundu resident magistrate last Friday and faced a second count of unlawfully sedating the complainant.Wachira did not have a lawyer. He denied both charges and was released on Sh200,000 bond and a surety of a similar amount. He was given the option of paying Sh100,000 bail.Prosecuting counsel Leah Kabiu did not raise any objection.The case will be mentioned on Wednesday next week and the hearing will be on May 15.